CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 22, 1958, pg. 3 reads: " Foxy, Eh? - That's what the judges thought, too, when they selected lovely Barbara Robinson of 7618 Susquehanna St., among the first 10 entrants (out of 87) in Press Photographer's Contest, Sunday at the Hotel Penn Sheraton.  A student at the Pittsburgh Playhouse, the 21-year-old Barbara collects proverbs as a hobby.  Oh, yes, her "orbit code" is 34-22-34 - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Barbara Robinson wearing light colored one piece bathing suit with sweetheart neckline, and open-toes shoes, holding a trophy with swimmer on top, standing in Penn Sheraton for Press Photographer's Contest
